commentTextItems.html: that is a huge hit- right out of the ground from O'Brien to finish proceedings. It was a good length delivery but O'Brien heaved it over the midwicket boundary.

commentPostTextItems.html: So that's it, Ireland are European Champions, winning at a canter by 7 wickets under the D/L Method. Thanks for all your patience today with the weather but we got there in the end.

Join us at the weekend for our coverage of the World Cup 20Twenty qualifier in Belfast. Coverage gets underway at 9am with the first game Scotland vs The Netherlands scheduled to start at 9.30am weather permitting of course.
That's all today from me, Chris Busby. Cheers
